title: The <span style="color: #000000;">**Center**</span> and the <span style="color: #c00000;">**Reichsbanner**</span>
new-page: true
subtitle: A new era of cooperation between the <span style="color: #000000;">We</span><span style="color: #DD0000;">im</span><span style="color: #FFCC00;">ar</span> coalition parties?
tags: event
view-if: year > 1930 and pro_republic < 50 and nsdap_r > 10 and left_strength > right_strength and left_strength > 25 and spd_r < 26
